" To be the best whether in sports, business or any other aspect of life, it's never enough just to get to the top, you have to stay there. And then you have to climb higher because there is always someone right behind you trying to catch up.
Most people are willing to settle for "good enough", but if you're relentless, those words mean nothing to you. Being the best means engineering your life and you never stop until you get what you want. And then you keep going until you get what's next. And then you go for even more.............
You refuse limitations. You quietly and forcefully do whatever it takes to get what you want. You understand the insatiable addiction to success.
You can read clever motivational slogans all day and still have no idea how to get where you want to be. Wanting something won't get you anywhere...... Trying to be someone you're not won't get you anywhere........ Waiting for someone or something to light your fire won't get you anywhere.......
Everything you need to be great is already inside you. All your ambitions, secrets, your darkest dreams. They're waiting for you to just let go. So what's stopping you. Most people give up because people told them what they can't do. And it's easier to stay safe in the comfort zone. So they sits on the fence unable to decide , unable to act .....
It's time to stop listening to what everyone else says about you , telling you what to do , how to act , how u should feel. Let them judge you by your results and nothing else. It's none of their business how you get where you're going. If you're relentless there is no half-way. No could, should or maybe. Don't tell me the glass is half full or half empty, you either have something in that glass or you don't . But if you don't make a choice, the choice will be made for you.
Be relentless in your pursuit for perfection. You won't ever be perfect, but in the process you will achieve greatness. Decide, Commit, Act, Succeed, Repeat................ ". #manofsteel #superman #henrycavill #movieprops #collectibles
